  <div class="footer">
    <p><img src="./assets/images/icon_512x512.png" alt="Logo" style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;background:#52C263;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" /><strong>Senior Sharp</strong> — Brain training specially designed for senior citizens</p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;">Available free on Google Play Store</p>
